messages.content: Okay, I'm ready. What's your first command?

thoughts.subject: Mapping the Landscape
thoughts.description: I'm currently focused on the existing Next.js project structure within the `studio` directory. My primary goal is to map the page organization in `studio/src/`. This initial assessment will inform how to best integrate the new page.

thoughts.subject: Charting the Course
thoughts.description: I've outlined the project structure assessment, focusing on `studio/src/app` to understand routing. Now I'm shifting to a step-by-step plan: listing files, directory creation (`claude-vertex-example`), and a basic page. Next, I'll examine `page.tsx` for layout and component usage, then adapt that style, adding a new navigation link to get the new page easily available.
